/**
 * Agent-Powered Seed Script
 *
 * Replaces hardcoded seed templates with data generated by the actual agent pipeline.
 * Each "vibe" (raw user input) flows through: subject line → decision makers → message → moderation → DB save.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   tsx scripts/seed-with-agents.ts
 *
 * Required env vars:
 *   GEMINI_API_KEY   - Gemini API for subject line, decision makers, message generation, quality moderation
 *
 * Optional env vars:
 *   GROQ_API_KEY     - Llama Guard safety moderation (skipped if absent)
 *   EXA_API_KEY      - Exa source discovery (falls back to Google grounding if absent)
 *   DATABASE_URL     - Database connection (defaults to local)
 */

